{"tid":796363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"睇見隔離個我不是新郎 反思現今社會婚姻係咪真係好野","createTime":"2018-08-27T17:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T13:10:39.000Z","uid":49544,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7f263b0b3eb0c74f17847a30d093ee5e79242695","tid":796363,"uid":49544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:51:15.000Z","msg":"睇見隔離Post<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/796197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/796197</a><br />\n她結婚但新郎不是我<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都Agger入面啲巴打講<br />\n<br />\n個女主咁樣做其實幾仆街 個老公依家唔綠遲早都綠<br />\n<br />\n但係靜落黎諗 其實世界上應該好多人都係咁 差在你有冇講出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時諗下 現代社會果種婚姻制度係咪真係對於男女感情嘅關係喺一樣好嘅野 <br />\n<br />\n點解做人唔可以啱就一齊唔啱就分開 永遠都要人一世同一個伴侶 唔可以一父多妻/一妻多夫<br />\n<br />\n其實諗下都係源於道德倫理，其實出軌呢個概念又係由幾時出現 又點解出現<br />\n<br />\n咁當然自己都係受到現代教育 都認為人係唔應該做出背叛另一半嘅事<br />\n<br />\n但係我認為依家果個社會制度對於愛情/感情嘅制肘已經好似有啲令到人反而冇得從感情/愛情中得到歡愉<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申多次：唔支持綠帽 出軌 純粹有感而發"},{"pid":"f3aa3d538804b60c45e6c2e348008ef423e88289","tid":796363,"uid":21558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"我係果個post話條女立心不良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好人好者臨結婚都撩鳩人<br />\n被班懷舊厹追住屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話我質疑樓主冇定力<br />\n<br />\n大佬啊<br />\n咁有定力就一笑置之啦<br />\n仲會開post咩<br />\n大家係男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現實又唔識，我特登唱條女咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條女擺明本身就係想留後路俾自己"},{"pid":"179a119bccda0fca85eae4df583e9b4f8008a846","tid":796363,"uid":132210,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:59:08.000Z","msg":"個人認為<br />\n婚姻制度係為左可以易啲管理 而唔係為左令人從中得到愉悅"},{"pid":"18be3535799980a5305b0b495520ef114cde87ec","tid":796363,"uid":21558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:00:28.000Z","msg":"好多事心知咪算<br />\n講到出口就出事架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難得果個post既樓主真係中哂計<br />\n講到又遺憾又悔恨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女人用呢啲橋真係萬試萬靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73f588b3c7d773ea56a0e7133d7ec44184d8dc6","tid":796363,"uid":126875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:22:14.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇女朋友？即係你覺得一夫一妻制令你感情生活有好多制肘係咪咁？"},{"pid":"1dc537e26dd1d9f3846434fc4eefe40da9f839b0","tid":796363,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:53:54.000Z","msg":"結唔到婚都可以做朋友者。<br />\n唔好過火位⋯<br />\n做一世朋友可能好過成為戀人。"},{"pid":"c204a5a584a264da585dab9b82bef1a0110d3d93","tid":796363,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T20:53:05.000Z","msg":"比起結婚，厹/<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既思維仲保守，有仔既女就唔鐘意得？感情唔係咁運作的～"},{"pid":"32779cfca607f59bdd9ef19296ae4f37c443935e","tid":796363,"uid":52408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3aa3d538804b60c45e6c2e348008ef423e88289","tid":796363,"uid":21558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:57:35.000Z",